Step 3 — Push to GitHub, Vercel auto-deploys.

Step 4 — Install on phone:

Android:

Open Chrome → go to your Vercel URL
Tap the 3 dots menu → "Add to Home Screen"
Done ✓
iPhone:

Open Safari → go to your Vercel URL
Tap the Share button → "Add to Home Screen"
Done ✓
The app will open fullscreen with no browser bar, just like a real app.



